CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 24, 1957, pg. B7 reads: "Senior Master Open Pair brought forth Sandy Gholston and Marion Griffis of Detroit to the winners' circle"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of senior master open pair winners Sandy Gholston and Marion Griffis, holding large trophy, posed in Fort Pitt Hotel for 24th annual American Bridge Association tournament
